OL,3,CWelsh Government propose end to 'tax-
OL,4,Cbreak' for private schools
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has unveiled
OL,7,Fplans to end a so-called 'tax-break'
OL,8,Fin fee-paying schools from April next
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FA consultation has been launched on
OL,12,Fthe proposals to withdraw charitable
OL,13,Fnon-domestic rates relief from private
OL,14,Fschools.
OL,16,FNon-domestic rates relief is
OL,17,Feffectively a reduction in business
OL,18,Frates for charitable organisations.
