OL,3,CWelsh Government propose end to 'tax-
OL,4,Cbreak' for private schools
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government have ear-marked
OL,7,Fthe funding raised by ending this tax
OL,8,Frelief to support local public
OL,9,Fservices.
OL,11,FFinance Secretary Mark Drakeford said:
OL,12,F"We believe that independent schools
OL,13,Fwith charitable status in Wales should
OL,14,Fbe treated in the same way as those
OL,15,Fwhich are not charities, which is why
OL,16,Fwe are proposing removing this tax
OL,17,Frelief.
