OL,3,CWelsh Government propose end to 'tax-
OL,4,Cbreak' for private schools
OL,6,F"It would bring Wales into line with
OL,7,FScotland and the UK Government is also
OL,8,Fplanning to make similar changes in
OL,9,FEngland."
OL,11,FIn Wales, private schools are
OL,12,Fregistered as independent schools, of
OL,13,Fwhich there are 83 across the country.
OL,15,F17 of these receive charitable non-
OL,16,Fdomestic rates relief, which is worth
OL,17,Faround #1.3m every year.
