OL,3,CWelsh Government propose end to 'tax-
OL,4,Cbreak' for private schools
OL,6,FThe consultation sets out the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment's proposal and asks for
OL,8,Fviews. It will run for 12 weeks from
OL,9,F23 September and responses are
OL,10,Frequested by 16 December 2024.
OL,12,FResponding to a consultation launch
OL,13,FTom Giffard MS, Welsh Conservative
OL,14,FShadow Education Minister, said:
OL,16,F"Labour's focus on private schools is
OL,17,Fa bias that will ultimately cost the
OL,18,Ftaxpayer in the long run.
