OL,3,CWelsh Government propose end to 'tax-
OL,4,Cbreak' for private schools
OL,6,F"With parents pulling their children
OL,7,Fout of private schools and placing
OL,8,Fthem into an already overwhelmed state
OL,9,Fschool system, not only will it cost
OL,10,Fthe taxpayer more, it will increase
OL,11,Fclass sizes and heap more pressure on
OL,12,Fthe hard working teaching staff.
OL,14,F"Labour's short-sighted thinking
OL,15,Freflects their wider ineptitude with
OL,16,Fthe economy, the Welsh Conservatives
OL,17,Fwill always prioritise our children's
OL,18,Feducation and appropriately fund our
OL,19,Fschools."
